Direct Known Subclasses:
DropdownDatePicker, DropdownTimePicker
public abstract class DropdownContainer
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.TextBox
implements HasDojo

Basic class of the widgets those associate an input and a popup window to display or edit a temporal information. So, is the baisc class of the components :

  • DropdownDatePicker
  • DropdownTimePicker

This component is an encapsulation GWT of Dojo components. Warning the widget exist under 3 faces :

  • a GWT widget (this!)
  • a Dojo widget (which play the role of 'this' for GWT)
  • a structur of DOM elements, the only exploitable presentation by the navigator.

Author:
Henry,Vianney
